        changed.</p>

      <div class='info-box'>
        <p><strong>‚úÖ What happened:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your password was changed</li>
          <li>All active sessions have been terminated</li>
          <li>You'll need to log in again on all devices</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='details'>
        <p><strong>Change Details:</strong></p>
        <p>üïê Time: {{timestamp}}</p>
        <p>üåê IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class='warning-box'>
        <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Didn't make this change?</strong></p>
        <p>If you didn't change your password, your account may be compromised.
          Please:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact our support team immediately</li>
          <li>Reset your password right away</li>
          <li>Review your recent account activity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
        <p>¬© 2026 Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>